<i>noun</i>: 증손자 [증손자], 증손녀 [증손녀], 증손 [증손] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>증손자 [증손자]</dt><br>
<dd>great-grandchild; great-grandson</dd><br>
<dd>손자의 아들. 또는 아들의 손자.</dd><br>
<dd>The son of one's grandchild, or the grandchild of one's son.</dd><br>
<dt>증손녀 [증손녀]</dt><br>
<dd>great-grandchild; great-granddaughter</dd><br>
<dd>손자의 딸. 또는 아들의 손녀.</dd><br>
<dd>The daughter of one's grandchild, or the granddaughter of one's son.</dd><br>
